{
  "stem": "22237.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Many times I came to school very late, just trying to avoid these Hitlerjugend.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In time, these children would get to know the Jewish children, and they would wait for them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And many times I had to pass another school, a non-Jewish school, and they would stand there waiting for me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They would th-- throw stones, not just at me, at many of the Jewish children.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I would have to find all kinds of ways to get to school in order to avoid either these Delinquent or the-- the-- the the other children in school.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I remember, I think it was 1935.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "When my brother used to take violin lessons, and one day, he wasn't home on time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When somebody wasn't home on time, we always worried, because we always wondered.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But nobody wanted to show the other person.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We didn't want our parents to worry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Nobody wanted anybody else to worry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I remember that I could-- I remember everybody looking at the clock, nobody saying much.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then I started-- I put my coat, and I went out, and I thought, let me see what happened to him.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Let me look for him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he was on the floor, with his violin broken in pieces.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the Hitlerjugend were beating him up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[SIGHS] It was terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And-- Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he made it home, and he had to recover from the-- from this incident.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was very hard to take.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I also, that particular year, I remember being in a-- in a bus coming home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At that time, I took the-- the-- the-- it wasn't a bus, it was a trolley, what today like a trolley car.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were also pushing me around in that bus.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
